732
01:06:17,900 --> 01:06:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Informatičar?

733
01:06:18,900 --> 01:06:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] Informatičar, ba, to sad.

734
01:06:19,900 --> 01:06:20,900
